{"tid":85590,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有發過清醒夢","createTime":"2017-01-18T12:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T19:37:41.000Z","uid":65256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5195554381ee82101ba070919f49b0aeaf6d0eb2","tid":85590,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:28:33.000Z","msg":"啱啱瞓果陣發咗個夢<br />\n夢入面好清楚有自己意識<br />\n我想玩過山車 跟住就玩咗<br />\n勁正 勁大離心力<br />\n但玩完之後 我嘗試去轉換場景 去條街飛<br />\n但失敗咗 我好似意識到自己清醒<br />\n慢慢relate番個人去現實 聽到電視聲同老母把聲<br />\n最後我意識到自己瞓係床<br />\n但輾轉反側咗陣 最後轉到一個位 我就醒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我瞓緊果陣應該冇郁過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdda4dc67476af20fb8a7843cba5f86a41cdd749","tid":85590,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:33:18.000Z","msg":"試過發到一半 <br />\n意識到自己發緊夢<br />\n之後我想點就點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e11546a0f7789b8da4643dc957ebc08262a6a1","tid":85590,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:37:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過發到一半 <br />\n意識到自己發緊夢<br />\n之後我想點就點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打做咗咩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a40ae7e197f7fba874535ec2d90b7af077c1985","tid":85590,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:39:10.000Z","msg":"發清醒夢仲去玩過山車<br />\ngay test pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28fa8e0007ccab3b2f0dd5458e2ed0cf9fc1bd78","tid":85590,"uid":31788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:39:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過發到一半 <br />\n意識到自己發緊夢<br />\n之後我想點就點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成日試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0948ced03038b114c9